Subject: [PATCH 309/634] ARM: fiq_glue: Add custom fiq return handler api.
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Change-Id: I5ff2764e85151ca0a88576542fda07c2d33dd065
